snippet.textDisplay:
Right now I am going through a lot in my life. This song makes me hopeful,i don't know of what kind but it does and it inspired me to write a poem /ode to my life situation right now. It's called HOPE

HOPE
As I sail through the deepest chambers of my sea 
Where I am neck dipped in water
My body feels numb and cold
Monsters of the sea cursing their lungs out
The memories of the shore I left giving me nightmares
My friends on the other end eyeing on me
Some vouching for me ,some erasing me from their memories
BUT here i am,
My soul is alive 
Sending impulses to my flesh
Pushing me through the waves to the land i belong to
Because I am the KHALASI
The sea belongs to me ,the land belongs to me
And i belong to HOPE
                                        ~~ 4607
